---
import LineaHombre from "./icons/LineaHombre.astro";
import Github from "./icons/Github.astro"
import Linkedin from "./icons/Linkedin.astro"
import Gmail from "./icons/Gmail.astro";
---

<section
    id="hero"
    class="scroll-mt-10 px-4 sm:px-8"
>
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-10 lg:gap-32 justify-center items-end max-w-5xl w-full mx-auto pt-10">

        <!-- Ilustración -->
        <div class="self-center mb-2 order-2 md:order-1 shrink-0">
            <LineaHombre class="w-56 sm:w-64 md:w-90 h-auto text-icon-stroke transition-colors duration-500" />
        </div>

        <!-- Contenido de texto -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-start gap-4 order-1 md:order-2 w-full">
            <span class="py-1 px-3 text-xs text-brand-primary rounded-full border border-brand-primary/30 bg-brand-primary/10 font-medium">
                Hola, soy
            </span>

            <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-text-main leading-tight">
                Joel Anderson <span class="text-brand-primary">Machaca Nina</span>
            </h1>

            <span class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-primary/90">
                Backend Developer
            </span>

            <p class="text-text-muted max-w-lg leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base">
                Desarrollador Full-Stack con enfoque en React, Angular y Spring Boot. Cuento con experiencia en ambos lados del stack, aunque mi mayor interés está en el diseño de APIs y la arquitectura backend. Me enfoco en escribir código bien estructurado, fácil de mantener y que resuelva el problema correcto.
            </p>

            <!-- Botones CTA -->
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-2 w-full">
                <a href="#proyectos" 
                   class="py-2 sm:py-3 px-5 sm:px-6 text-btn-text rounded-2xl bg-btn-fill hover:bg-brand-hover transition-all hover:scale-105 shadow-lg shadow-brand-primary/20 font-bold text-sm sm:text-base">
                   Ver proyectos
                </a>
                <a href="#contacto"
                   class="py-2 sm:py-3 px-5 sm:px-6 text-btn-ghost-text rounded-2xl border border-btn-ghost-border hover:bg-brand-primary/10 transition-all font-bold text-sm sm:text-base">
                   Contáctame
                </a>
                <a href="/CV-JoelMachaca-developer.pdf"
                download 
                   class="py-2 sm:py-3 px-5 sm:px-6 text-btn-ghost-text rounded-2xl border border-btn-ghost-border hover:bg-brand-primary/10 transition-all font-bold text-sm sm:text-base">
                   Mi CV
                </a>
            </div>

            <!-- Redes sociales -->
            <div class="flex justify-center items-center gap-4 sm:gap-5 mt-4 p-3 rounded-2xl bg-bg-card border border-border-subtle shadow-sm">
                <a href="https://github.com/JoelDev2002" 
                   class="text-text-main hover:text-brand-primary transition-colors transform hover:scale-110" 
                   target="_blank">
                   <Github class="w-6 h-6 sm:w-8 sm:h-8"/>
                </a>
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/joel-machaca/" 
                   class="text-text-main hover:text-brand-primary transition-colors transform hover:scale-110" 
                   target="_blank">
                   <Linkedin class="w-8 h-8 sm:w-10 sm:h-10" />
                </a>
                <a href="mailto:joel.machaca01@gmail.com" 
                   class="text-text-main hover:text-brand-primary transition-colors transform hover:scale-110" 
                   target="_blank">
                   <Gmail class="w-6 h-6 sm:w-8 sm:h-8" />
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>